Enum Class ParamMap.Type

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<ParamMap.Type>
io.github.ericmedvet.jnb.core.ParamMap.Type
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<ParamMap.Type>, Constable
Enclosing interface:
ParamMap
public static enum ParamMap.Type extends Enum<ParamMap.Type>
The type of values that can be stored in a ParamMap. Besides the enum name, each Type has a short string representation obtainable with rendered(), useful for documenting and debugging builders in a NamedBuilder. Each constant is associated with a Java type, which is the actual one returned (if possible) by ParamMap.value(String, Type).
